scoreboard/                     ‚Üê workspace root
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ apps/
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ frontend/               ‚Üê Vite app (React + UI) (@scoreboard/frontend)
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ mobile/                 ‚Üê Expo app (React Native) (@scoreboard/mobile)
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ backend/                ‚Üê NestJS API (@scoreboard/backend)
