‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ packages/
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ core/                   ‚Üê @scoreboard/core ‚Äî DDD domain + application layer
‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ shared/                 ‚Üê shared code (future)
